menu "Wi-Fi manager"

    config WIFI_MANAGER_DEV_SSID
        string "Development Wi-Fi SSID (optional, do not commit)"
        default ""
        help
            If set, this network is saved as a profile on first boot
            (unless a profile with this SSID already exists), so hardware
            bring-up works without a settings UI yet. Set this only via
            menuconfig, in your local sdkconfig - sdkconfig is gitignored.
            Never put real credentials in sdkconfig.defaults.

    config WIFI_MANAGER_DEV_PASSWORD
        string "Development Wi-Fi password (optional, do not commit)"
        default ""
        help
            Password for WIFI_MANAGER_DEV_SSID. Same rule: local
            sdkconfig only, never sdkconfig.defaults.

endmenu
